00:20:00,348 --> 00:20:02,919
hot zi zikh nisht gut oyfgefirt.

247
00:20:04,747 --> 00:20:07,543
un ikh hob gehat seykhl, dertsu,

248
00:20:07,615 --> 00:20:12,926
ikh hob nisht gezogt farn tate vi azoy zi iz shlekht tsu mir.

249
00:20:13,724 --> 00:20:16,537
von, ikh hob nisht gevolt se zol zayn,

250
00:20:17,572 --> 00:20:20,604
in der shtub, nisht BESEDER.

251
00:20:22,904 --> 00:20:25,177
