00:21:01,334 --> 00:21:04,175
hob ikh mikh nor mit dem geshpilt.

261
00:21:04,501 --> 00:21:07,314
andere meydelekh hobn zikh geshpilt,

262
00:21:07,387 --> 00:21:09,637
zey hobn gemakht a BUBE,

263
00:21:09,637 --> 00:21:14,149
zey hobn gemakht kleynikeytn, ober ikh nisht.

264
00:21:14,575 --> 00:21:17,405
un nebekh, mayn babe,

265
00:21:17,832 --> 00:21:20,848
hot gezogt az ikh bin shoyn,

266
00:21:20,971 --> 00:21:23,514
alts kleynervayz oys,

267
00:21:23,654 --> 00:21:28,003
az ikh farnem mikh mit ernste zakhn.

268
00:21:29,037 --> 00:21:35,867
un azoy iz es geven, ikh hob mikh mit ernste zakhn farnumen ad-hayom.

269
00:21:38,589 --> 00:21:47,764
vi azoy iz geven dos lebn ven Hitler iz oyfgeshtanen, in nayntsn dray un draysik?

