ikh hob gehat a shvester, nebekh, di klenere shvester mayne, mit zeks kinder.

285
00:23:00,483 --> 00:23:02,942
un se iz gekumen an ungar,

286
00:23:03,622 --> 00:23:07,262
un er hot zey aroysgevorfn fun ir shtub,

287
00:23:07,807 --> 00:23:09,827
un zi hot gevoynt,

288
00:23:10,017 --> 00:23:16,830
zi hot nebekh, er hot zey arayngeshtelt in a kleyn, kleyn kamerl.

289
00:23:17,358 --> 00:23:21,335
vos fir kinder zenen geshlofn in eyn bet.

290
00:23:21,999 --> 00:23:25,352
un zi iz in an andern bet geshlofn,

291
00:23:25,627 --> 00:23:29,756
ober zeyer shver hot di betn plats gehat.

292
00:23:31,449 --> 00:23:35,544
un se iz geven erger vi shlekht.

293
00:23:36,393 --> 00:23:40,387
un dernokh dem hot zikh ongefangen di deportirn.

294
00:23:42,687 --> 00:23:45,821
ikh, ikh bin oyfgevaksn,

295
00:23:46,653 --> 00:23:52,622
hob ikh mikh farnumen mit a bisl sokhreray.

296
00:23:54,854 --> 00:23:57,600
un ikh hob mir tsamgeb-,

297
00:23:57,723 --> 00:23:59,743
ikh hob mikh basheftikt,

298
00:24:00,828 --> 00:24:11,066
ikh hob gebrengt fun Tshekhay, fun Slovakay, farshidene zakhn.

299
00:24:12,708 --> 00:24:18,879
un ikh hob, in Rumenye dos zeyer gut farkoyft. un kh'hob sheyn gelt fardint.

300
00:24:19,171 --> 00:24:26,405
un ikh hob mir gekoyft a sakh shtafir, ikh hob dokh nisht gehat fun vemen tsu vartn.

301
00:24:27,102 --> 00:24:30,084
oykh ikh, oykh an andere shvester,

302
00:24:30,511 --> 00:24:36,311
azoy az dey, kh'hob gehat tsvey groyse kastn mit zakhn.

303
00:24:36,822 --> 00:24:39,062
un, nisht kleydung.

304
00:24:40,788 --> 00:24:45,997
ibertsikhn, tishtekher, azolekhike zakhn,

305
00:24:47,133 --> 00:24:56,021
un se iz gekumen zeyer a shlekhter ungarisher, un er hot genumen ale zakhn,

306
00:24:56,448 --> 00:25:00,324
un avekge-, avekgenumen far zikh.

307
00:25:01,409 --> 00:25:04,020
deys iz geven bay mayn shvester.

308
00:25:04,109 --> 00:25:06,889
ober di zakhn zenen mayn geven.

309
00:25:08,581 --> 00:25:17,014
un azoy hob ikh gehat iberbet, un farshidene zakhn, oykh bay mayn shvester,

310
00:25:17,221 --> 00:25:19,342
oyvn oyfn boydem.

311
00:25:19,432 --> 00:25:21,890
geton oyf azoy a shtang.

312
00:25:24,528 --> 00:25:26,160
ales avekgenumen.

313
00:25:26,283 --> 00:25:28,995
un dernokh dem hot men zey avekgenumen.

314
00:25:30,519 --> 00:25:33,585
un nisht tsurikgebrengt. a shokhnte,

315
00:25:34,822 --> 00:25:38,245
zeyer a fayne froy, a goyte,

316
