aza proste, nisht keyn shtudirte,

317
00:25:42,449 --> 00:25:47,929
hot genumen a tikhl ire, a groyse, a shal,

318
00:25:49,081 --> 00:25:53,194
un in zayt fun shal,

319
00:25:54,616 --> 00:25:57,379
hot zi arayngeneyt gelt.

320
00:25:58,447 --> 00:26:02,998
az efsher kumt on ergets tsu mayn shvester

321
00:26:03,813 --> 00:26:08,246
zol zi ober z-, zey zenen geven aynfarshtanen.

322
00:26:09,213 --> 00:26:14,574
az zi zol, fun dort, az zi hot dort gelt.

323
00:26:15,507 --> 00:26:19,670
ober men hot nisht gelozt. zi hot es, di shal,

324
00:26:19,743 --> 00:26:24,294
arayngetrogn in geto, far mayn shvester.

325
00:26:25,734 --> 00:26:29,458
un me hot ir tsurikgevorfn der shal.

326
00:26:29,969 --> 00:26:35,128
un nokh dem, nokh mitog, hot zi gebakn broyt, dey goyte,

327
00:26:35,707 --> 00:26:40,123
un zi hot arayngeton in broyt

328
00:26:41,343 --> 00:26:46,772
